{"tid":132754,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"忙裡偷閒 紅女巫品嚐冰淇淋 素顏光滑肌膚宛如少女","createTime":"2017-02-24T05:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T18:07:30.000Z","uid":9573,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88e790448bb38951ff16d711644fd70b67bd604b","tid":132754,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:22:45.000Z","msg":"以MARVEL女性超級英雄角色「緋紅女巫」走紅全球的美國女演員Elizabeth Olsen不只在電影中展現了迷人的角色魅力，在戲外她開朗的個性和公認的美貌也讓影迷更加迷戀她，同時在去年《美國隊長 3》（Captain America: Civil War）首映會上，伊莉莎白&middot;歐森也透過上面這一襲白色的禮服向眾人展現她隱藏的豐滿上圍，連美國隊長在首映會上也忍不住盯著瞧，現在以下可能又多了一個會讓你更愛Elizabeth的事情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62951/58aced8e897a4.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62951%2F58aced8e897a4.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=0fa543eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已經持續幾周在洛杉磯進行《復仇者聯盟 3》（Avengers: Infinity War）拍攝的Elizabeth Olsen，在這周一被記者發現她忙裡偷閒，現身在加州 Studio City 的一家 McConnell's Scoop 冰淇淋店，獨自在店內開心品嘗冰淇淋加餅乾的組合。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62951/58aced899e7cc.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62951%2F58aced899e7cc.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=36e43869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼在 2 月 16 日剛度過 28 歲生日，簡單穿著黑色大衣搭配牛仔褲上街，素顏的她展現了絕佳狀態的好膚質。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62951/58aced8ba783d.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62951%2F58aced8ba783d.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=f6147a79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼冰淇淋實在太美味，讓她忍不住露出了幸福的表情，這一瞬間的搞笑表情似乎可以成為網友的「表情包」惡搞素材。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62951/58aced8c7ba69.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62951%2F58aced8c7ba69.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=108e19e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62951/58aced87c4bec.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62951%2F58aced87c4bec.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=5d63adfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼因為吃到好吃的，伊莉莎白忍不住立刻低頭再挑選其他口味。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62951/58aced8d7694f.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62951%2F58aced8d7694f.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=203e7946&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼步出冰淇淋店的她還外帶了餅乾，透過這一張抿嘴的可愛表情，可以看出皮膚光滑到說是十幾歲的少女也不為過，可愛的酒窩更是讓人羨慕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62951/58aced88ad748.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62951%2F58aced88ad748.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=b0106df1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除了《復仇者聯盟 3》，與「鷹眼」Jeremy Renner共演的電影《Wind River》也在今年上映，而《復仇者聯盟 3》則是預計於 2018 年 5 月 4 日上映，相信大家都很期待能夠盡快看見緋紅女巫的身影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62951/58aced8a9ff3d.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62951%2F58aced8a9ff3d.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=bcc04403&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"966c30cfa1f3bfdded6c1cb1204fc954c7d5c7dc","tid":132754,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T06:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fd4c86315acb7a03be5e446e4ca0b0cedd2511","tid":132754,"uid":8048,"like":0,"disl